name: KLM A330-303 departure from Calgary
description:
Happy heavy aircraft Friday!
First of all, this video is dedicated to jelmerpilotHD! Please check out his awesome channel here: www.youtube.com/jelmerpilotHD

Second of all, thank you SO much for 400 subscribers! I can't believe I got so many in such a short time! Big thanks to all of you :D

This video features a KLM Airbus A330-303 departing Calgary International Airport on its daily flight to Amsterdam. This is another one of my old videos that I never got around to uploading, so that's the both the old watermark and old intro are in this video. Listen to that spool-up, too! I hope you enjoy it!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
